		<p>Ever considered looking into offloading some of the traffic, at least on the early days of a release, into archive.org? At least the CC releases are allowed to be hosted in there for like ever, and it&#8217;s as future proof as it gets on the internet. Not sure what linking freedom you get however, probably not hotlinking. Worth a shot tough.</p>

